                        ดูรายละเอียดทุกข้อ
                    </button>
                    <button onclick="restartCurrentPart()" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold px-5 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-sm transition text-sm flex items-center justify-center">
                        ทำใหม่อีกครั้ง
                    </button>
                    <button onclick="exitToDashboard()" class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold px-5 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-sm transition text-sm flex items-center justify-center">
